public class OrderedNonUniqueIndex<K extends java.lang.Comparable<K>,T>
extends NonUniqueIndex<K,T>
implements StdMultiMap<K,Record<T>>

The index is sorted in order of specified field. 

    Specifying field is allowed overlapping.

hiroaki.kubota@mail.rakuten.co.jp
